#: src/templates/about.html:21
msgid ""
"PDE est une plateforme de révision qui regroupe des quiz (QCM), des notes"
" et des reviews pour la certification Google Cloud Professional Data "
"Engineer. Tu peux parcourir les thèmes, lancer des quiz par catégorie et "
"utiliser la recherche pour retrouver rapidement un sujet."
msgstr ""
"PDE is a revision platform that brings together quiz (QCM), notes and "
"reviews for the Google Cloud Professional Data Engineer certification. "
"You can browse topics, run quizzes by category and use search to quickly "
"find a subject."

#: src/templates/about.html:24
msgid "Certification Google Cloud"
msgstr "Google Cloud Certification"

#: src/templates/about.html:25
